name: Chihiro Inu
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
To develop a token that add value to holders in decentralised nance space, and trusted. We committed to full what has been planned and promised to the community since the beginning.

This is the De Fi token where it was born from the community focus and
will be built based on the community trust and engagement.
